OL,7,Fdevastating, that the first time she
OL,8,Ftold it to me I was lost for words.
OL,10,FEven though a camera was filming our
OL,11,Finterview, I couldn't think of what to
OL,12,Fsay next.
OL,14,FHere is the short version.
OL,16,FIn 1981, Denise and her husband Colin
OL,17,Fhad a son called Lee. As a baby he was
