OL,3,CBlood scandal: 'You watch your child
OL,4,Cjust disappearing before your eyes'
OL,6,FWhen he was two years old, Lee was
OL,7,Fgiven a blood product called 'Factor
OL,8,F8'. The batch Lee was treated with was
OL,9,Finfected with HIV.
OL,11,FAround the time he turned seven Lee
OL,12,Fstarted to get ill. He had trouble
OL,13,Fhearing, some days he couldn't see,
OL,14,Fothers he had so many ulcers in his
OL,15,Fthroat that he couldn't eat.
OL,17,FHe had AIDS.
OL,19,FDenise said it was awful to watch:
OL,20,F"You watch your child just
OL,21,Fdisappearing before your eyes."
