OL,6,FThere was such a in the 1980s that the
OL,7,Ffamily had to move to a different part
OL,8,Fof the country where they weren't
OL,9,Fknown.
OL,11,FWhen Lee was eight years old he asked
OL,12,FDenise what was going to happen to
OL,13,Fhim, "He asked in the end. He asked:
OL,14,F'Am I going to die?'"
OL,16,FDenise was honest: "I did say 'I'm not
OL,17,Fsure,' but I did say 'most probably
OL,18,F... we don't know.'"
OL,20,FLee died in January 1992 - he was ten.
